292
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:10,600
It is a pity for these women.

293
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:13,490
I will make those demons pay with their blood.

294
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:21,400
Folks of Luoxian Town!

295
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,360
Come out, everyone.

296
00:13:23,800 --> 00:13:25,440
I have something to say.

297
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:28,640
People of Luoxian Town!

298
00:13:29,160 --> 00:13:30,440
Follow me!

299
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:32,160
It has begun.

300
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:37,600
Folks of Luoxian Town!

301
00:13:37,760 --> 00:13:40,120
The village head has already started gathering the people.

302
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:41,250
Let's go take a look.

303
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:50,720
Everyone.

304
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:52,600
We live here in Luoxian Town.

305
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:55,080
We don't seek wealth or power.

306
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:57,520
All we want is to live and work in peace.

307
00:13:58,960 --> 00:14:00,690
But the Lin family is inhumane.

308
00:14:01,160 --> 00:14:02,400
They collude with demons

309
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:04,760
and harm the people of our town.

310
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:06,480
What the Lin family takes away

311
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:08,400
are our daughters and sons,

312
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:11,920
our parents and wives.

313
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:13,720
They are so heartless.

314
00:14:14,160 --> 00:14:15,720
As the town chief,

315
00:14:17,400 --> 00:14:18,800
I can't stand it anymore.

316
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:22,920
Why don't you give your brother a chance?

317
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:25,360
He's been trying very hard.

318
00:14:26,880 --> 00:14:29,010
Life doesn't offer that many chances.

319
00:14:29,160 --> 00:14:30,320
Once you fail,

320
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:32,920
the price is the destruction of the Lin family.

321
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:37,720
Come.

322
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:38,840
Here.

323
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:40,960
Sign my name.

324
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:42,250
How dare you!

325
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:43,280
Lin Mo,

326
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,160
what are you trying to do?

327
00:14:44,160 --> 00:14:45,640
Say one more word of nonsense,

328
00:14:45,640 --> 00:14:47,240
or get up from that seat,

329
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:49,760
and I'll throw you into the well immediately,

330
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:51,680
just like you did to my mother.

331
00:14:56,320 --> 00:14:57,920
How could this be?

332
00:14:58,720 --> 00:15:00,840
You are extremely talented,

333
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:02,320
but you've been cowardly since childhood.

334
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:03,520
You didn't know how to say no,

335
00:15:03,520 --> 00:15:04,800
and never rebelled.

336
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:06,680
In everything,

337
00:15:06,680 --> 00:15:08,560
you yielded to Lin Fan.

338
00:15:08,560 --> 00:15:11,360
Why are you so tough now?

339
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:12,000
What?

340
00:15:12,640 --> 00:15:14,560
I didn't grow up as you expected,

341
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:15,770
so you're not happy?

342
00:15:17,680 --> 00:15:18,960
Sign here.

343
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:21,240
Let's have a smooth handover first.

344
00:15:21,240 --> 00:15:22,320
As for the rest of the score,

345
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,720
we'll settle it slowly.

346
00:15:24,680 --> 00:15:25,120
You...

347
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:26,840
Butler!

348
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:28,520
Butler!

349
00:15:28,760 --> 00:15:29,800
The pharmacy manager.

350
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:31,760
I don't know why you insisted on coming back.

351
00:15:31,760 --> 00:15:33,160
But if you want to achieve your goal,

352
00:15:33,160 --> 00:15:33,760
except me,

353
00:15:33,880 --> 00:15:35,010
nobody can help you.

354
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:47,050
Why do I feel like a villain?

355
00:15:47,480 --> 00:15:48,520
Father, Mother.

356
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:49,800
Lord Governor,

357
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:50,480
over here.

358
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:52,280
A new storyline has been triggered.

